598
00:45:35,000 --> 00:45:40,000
Dengbêj û xwandavan e, karker û cûtkar û zane.
 
Bards and readers, workers and farmers and wise ones.

599
00:45:40,000 --> 00:45:45,000
Dengbêj û xwandavan e, karker û cûtkar û zane.
 
Bards and readers, workers and farmers and wise ones.

600
00:45:45,000 --> 00:45:51,000
